# draw-order pins for options-over-mainmenu (1280x720, options slide-in settled).
# the options panel spans x=82..709; the mainmenu logo cube sits centered (boot color
# #eaeaea at screen center). avoid the panel/logo EDGES: edge pixels carry AA jitter
# and the logo pulses to wall-clock music (cost one rejected point at 0.6 0.5).
# options row background above the menu logo at the overlap point (if the base screen
# ever draws above the overlay band, this reads the logo's #eaeaea instead)
0.5 0.5 1f1f1f 8
# solid logo interior peeking right of the panel edge = the base still draws beneath
0.61 0.5 eaeaea 8
